node.text:
𝗣𝗿𝗲𝘀𝗲𝗻𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗠𝗰𝗠𝘂𝗮𝗳𝗳𝗶𝗻. Springy pork sausage patty loaded with spices, crusty homemade English muffins and a fluffy egg.
-
𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗱𝗶𝗳𝗳𝗲𝗿𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗲𝗿? 𝗖𝗵𝗲𝗱𝗱𝗮𝗿. Damn sonnn. 😩 Its galvanising sharpness performed miracles with the heartiness — cutting through but also bringing out the umami.
-
I think this is better than the real McCoy. But that fuss-free unhealthy indulgence the golden arches provide? That's a service missed by all, and I don't even eat it often. 🤷🏻‍♂️
-
Recipe Rating: 𝗠𝗖𝗗𝗢𝗡𝗔𝗟𝗗'𝗦 𝗕𝗘 𝗕𝗔𝗖𝗞 𝗦𝗢𝗢𝗡 quite a 5️⃣/5️⃣ tbh .
.
